tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE ProteomicsData (
  sample_id INT,
  protein_name VARCHAR(255),
  peptide_sequence TEXT,
  spectra_intensity FLOAT,
  is_biomarker BOOLEAN
);

CREATE TABLE Proteins (
  protein_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  protein_name TEXT,
  gene_name TEXT,
  molecular_weight FLOAT,
  isoelectric_point FLOAT
);

CREATE TABLE Proteins (
    protein_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    protein_name VARCHAR(255),
    protein_sequence TEXT,
    molecular_weight DECIMAL(10,2),
    protein_length INT
);

CREATE TABLE Samples (
    sample_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    sample_name VARCHAR(255),
    sample_type VARCHAR(50),
    sample_volume DECIMAL(10,2),
    sample_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE Experiments (
    experiment_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    experiment_name VARCHAR(255),
    experiment_type VARCHAR(50),
    experiment_date DATE,
    result_id INT
);

CREATE TABLE Gene (
    gene_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    gene_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    chromosome_id INT,
    start_position INT,
    end_position INT
);

CREATE TABLE Experiment (
    experiment_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    study_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    researcher_name VARCHAR(255),
    start_date DATE,
    end_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE Proteins (
  protein_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  protein_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
  gene_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
  molecular_weight FLOAT,
  function TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE Peptides (
  peptide_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  peptide_sequence TEXT NOT NULL,
  protein_id UUID REFERENCES Proteins(protein_id),
  location VARCHAR(100)
)

CREATE TABLE Experiments (
  experiment_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  experiment_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
  researcher_name VARCHAR(255),
  start_date DATE,
  end_date DATE
)

CREATE TABLE Samples (
  sample_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  sample_name VARCHAR(255),
  experiment_id UUID REFERENCES Experiments(experiment_id),
  date_collected DATE
)

CREATE TABLE Results (
  result_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  experiment_id UUID REFERENCES Experiments(experiment_id),
  sample_id UUID REFERENCES Samples(sample_id),
  protein_id UUID REFERENCES Proteins(protein_id),
  peptide_id UUID REFERENCES Peptides(peptide_id),
  result_value FLOAT
)
